        "Projektname": "Explonaut",
        "Jahr": 2015,
        "Titelbild": "Explonaut-Videostill.png (https://v5.airtableusercontent.com/v1/17/17/1685498400000/BFQkixd0BfV7jpIlYmNraQ/C7lgob9w10ZhdPSVmgpPL3DFvEIJtJMKP2bHDsh8FbOSVS5B2OzqaEmBINGALUB93WZyXg8NTLpp4Ppkzi_l_nm8U8vb7ucRm_xXhTLNens/s58tO0oIJE4x0_oTir3HN7OMiOK37wFfpSyTrd7LZJc)",
        "TextBeschreibung": "“Explonaut” is a concept of a scientific augmented-reality-game\nabout astronomy. The mainidea of “Explonaut” is about astromony\nbecoming something personal for the player. The user gets\ncontrol of an own virtual expedition-spaceship including an astronaut,\nwhich sets out for planets of our solar system. The spaceship\nflies in a realtime-augmented-realtiy-area to planets, how\nthey are currently being seen in the sky and explores them bit\nby bit. Every successful expedition enables a scientific aspect in\nthe logbook, which guaranties new achievements in later missions,\nif it is correctly understood by the player.\nMissions constists out of complex questions, which can‘t be solved\nin a single expedition, like “Why is life possible on earth?”\nAfterwards the player has to approach the correct planets and\nalso need to understand the received knowedge rightly to successfully\ncomplete the journey.\nIn “Explonaut” the player slips into the role of an explorer, scientist\nand discoverer to acquire the understanding of our solar systems\nastronomy.",
