        "TextBeschreibung": "Retikulum is an objective visual history book whose author is the citizens in Turkey. It shows the events, happenings and the relations between them before, after and during the Gezi Resistance according to the twitter data which is related to the resistance, away from any censorship concerns. The content of the book does not need an approval of any hierarchical authority, and all the information is constructed by the peoples’ tweet contents. The relations between the historical string of events are shown in a reticular structure based on the use of 2 different words in each content together.",
